properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 24 at 10:13PM AKST until January 25 at 6:00AM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations of 2 to 4 inches.
Total snow accumulations of 4 to 6 inches.

* WHERE...The Northeast Gulf Coast including Yakutat.

* WHEN...Until 6 AM AKST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. Travel could be
hazardous.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 AM AKST SATURDAY FOR YAKUTAT
